videos.description: Georgia's Anthony Edwards cruises past Auburn defenders for the easy layup.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards effortlessly gets to the rim) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards effortlessly gets to the rim

videos.description: Anthony Edwards puts up a deep 3-pointer over an Auburn defender and buries it.
videos.headline: Edwards sinks the deep 3-pointer

videos.description: Auburn blocks Anthony Edwards on the defensive end, leading to a fast-break alley-oop from J'Von McCormick to Devan Cambridge.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick lobs to Cambridge for Auburn alley-oop) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCormick lobs to Cambridge for Auburn alley-oop

videos.description: Auburn's J'Von McCormick drains the straightaway 3-pointer from long-range.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (McCormick pulls up from deep for Auburn) 2020/02/19 ESHEEET

videos.headline: McCormick pulls up from deep for Auburn

videos.description: Georgia's Anthony Edwards gets ahead of the defense in transition and breaks away for the slam.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards slips free for the breakaway dunk) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards slips free for the breakaway dunk

videos.description: Anthony Edwards buries a deep 3-pointer late in the second half which propels Georgia to the 65-55 upset of No. 13 Auburn.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Edwards puts exclamation point on Georgia's upset of Auburn) 2020/02/19 ESHEET

videos.headline: Edwards puts exclamation point on Georgia's upset of Auburn
